            Reach out to me publicly by <i>@dding</i> me at <a href="https://twitter.com/sakul6499" class="has-text-grey-dark">@Sakul6499</a> or contact me privately via PMs!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="columns mx-2 my-2">
      <div class="column card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="media">
            <div class="media-left">
              <figure class="image is-48x48">
                {% include "components/svg/keybase" %}
              </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="media-content">
